1
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:10,260
=Dungeon Archive=

2
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:12,320
The killer of the case is...

3
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:14,720
Leader Li.

4
00:00:14,780 --> 00:00:16,940
(Area lockdown successful)

5
00:00:17,180 --> 00:00:18,580
(Case unresolved: escape unsuccessful)

6
00:00:18,580 --> 00:00:20,140
(Leader Li)

7
00:00:20,140 --> 00:00:22,140
(Case reconstruction)

8
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:24,560
(Leader Li)
I'm the culprit, Leader Li.

9
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:27,520
A feared manager in the AI compound.

10
00:00:27,520 --> 00:00:29,360
I do anything for money,

11
00:00:29,360 --> 00:00:30,200
but in the end

12
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:32,200
(Tui Nengzao)
I was merely a pawn for Tui Nengzao.

13
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:34,280
Under his order,

14
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:35,360
we used illegal AI products

15
00:00:35,360 --> 00:00:37,600
to carry out customized romance scams

16
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:38,560
to rake in huge profits.

17
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:38,860
(Successful cases)

18
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:41,640
Although I got generous bonuses,

19
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:43,320
I started

20
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,720
to feel uneasy inside.

21
00:00:45,480 --> 00:00:46,440
The victims

22
00:00:46,440 --> 00:00:48,640
became shadows that haunted me

23
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,200
in my dreams.

24
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,360
Since the end of March,

25
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:52,640
I repeatedly told Tui Nengzao

26
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:54,800
(Mr. Tui, I've not been doing too well.)
my wish to leave the compound.

27
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:55,440
(Can I resign?)

28
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:56,360
(Mr. Tui, I can't do this anymore.)
I didn't know

29
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,880
(You did all these yourself.)
it would anger him.

30
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:58,260
(You won't live if others find out!)

31
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:00,040
He used what I've done

32
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:01,420
(To the ends of earth. Forever)
in the past

33
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:02,880
(You're in my hands. Destroy. Unless I die)
to threaten me.

34
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,920
He also intimidated me

35
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:06,360
and took my phone away.

36
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:08,640
On the night of April 6th,

37
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:10,680
I decided to gamble it all.

38
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:13,080
If he won't let me leave,

39
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:14,800
I'll bring him down with me.

40
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:16,640
During the day, I still pretended

41
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,280
to pressure employees
into working as usual.

42
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,400
At 9:40PM,

43
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:21,600
I saw Tui Nengzao

44
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,680
leaving through the security channel

45
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,840
without security.

46
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,200
It was the perfect opportunity
to strike,

47
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,400
so I quietly followed him.

48
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,560
The channel's design

49
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,640
allows one to access any one
of the other channels

50
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,480
and go back to the entrance.

51
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,640
(April 6th, 2026)
At 10PM,

52
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,360
I went through Channel Three

53
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,240
to the entrance.

54
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,600
I was about to leave

55
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,800
when I saw Tui Nengzao
lingering beside a woman

56
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:44,000
lying on the ground in the faint light.

57
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,720
He saw me

58
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:47,320
and drove me back to the entrance.

59
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,480
What are you doing here?

60
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,600
I gave him one last ultimatum,

61
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:53,760
accusing him of forcing me
to take part in child trafficking.

62
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,680
I wanted to stop.

63
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,800
But he brushed it off,

64
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:59,600
and wanted me to help him
lure another group of children.

65
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:01,360
He then tapped his badge

66
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,600
and entered the channel.

67
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,600
Since he won't let me out,

68
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,200
I wasn't going to let him live either.

69
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,880
I decided to make my move.

70
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,080
I remembered

71
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,920
dropping my bracelet a few days ago

72
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:12,760
when passing by the exit.

73
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,560
While picking up the beads,

74
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,600
I discovered a locked box.

75
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,460
(Change six of it to change 12345 to 23456)
The lid was marked

76
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:20,040
(This blueprint is interesting)
with the channel's design.

77
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,680
(It might come in handy)

78
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,120
After studying it carefully,

79
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,520
I uncovered the box's pin.

80
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,560
(Exit, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6: hidden door, entrance)
The corners could be adjusted,

81
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,800
allowing the routes to be shifted.

82
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,880
I open the box

83
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:32,760
to find a remote control
for the hidden door, a manual,

84
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,470
(Only I know the design)
and Tui Nengzao's handwriting.

85
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,880
(No one can know)
It said only he knows

86
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:36,840
the mechanism.

87
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,480
To prevent others from finding out,

88
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:42,400
(Change six of it to change 12345 to 23456)
I even removed the sticky note after studying the box.

89
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:44,040
Using what I had discovered,

90
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,840
(Leave no clues. Clear suspicion)
the perfect plan to escape suspicion

91
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,080
(Perfect plan)
began to take shape in my mind.

92
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,280
(Alibi)

93
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:51,520
Only Channel One can be used
for a single-person entry.

94
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:55,080
So I entered and followed him quickly.

95
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,560
(April 6th, 2026)
At 10:10PM,

96
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,880
I arrived at the exit

97
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,360
and saw Tui Nengzao's lackey leaving

98
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,120
(Exit)
after chatting briefly with him.

99
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,600
He was alone. The timing was perfect.

100
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:09,080
I hurried after Tui Nengzao.
Ready to make my move.

101
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,040
(Mr. Tui, I've not been doing too well.)
Even since I asked to leave,

102
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,800
(Mr. Tui, I can't do this anymore.)
I've been

103
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,720
(Every time I close my eyes, I see the old lady and the little boy.)
carrying

104
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,760
a bottle of Knockout drops with me.

105
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:15,660
(Knockout drops)

106
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,520
I stepped forward
and caught him off guard,

107
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,360
knocking him out

108
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,480
and dragged him back to the exit.

109
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,000
(Exit)
At 10:20PM,

110
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,680
I opened the box

111
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,800
with what I remembered

112
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,560
(Manual. Remote control)

113
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,680
and took the remote control inside.

114
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:30,240
(Manual)
Then I locked it again and put it back.

115
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,040
(Please press to open the exit door)
I pressed the exit door switch

116
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,360
and dragged the unconscious Tui Nengzao

117
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,920
to the corner of Channel One.

118
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,200
Then I entered 90 degrees
using the remote control.

119
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,920
After all the hidden doors rotated,

120
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,160
(Exit, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5,
6: hidden door, entrance)

121
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,640
I hid him inside the concealed space

122
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:45,480
(Corpse)
behind Channel One.

123
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:48,200
I planned to kill him
after the six new employees

124
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:50,080
entered the channel tomorrow.

125
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:52,280
Only Tui Nengzao know

126
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,240
the channel's mechanism.

127
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,280
The new employees

128
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,600
would see me

129
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,280
entering the channel with them.

130
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:01,280
They would be my alibi.

131
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,080
So no matter which channel I took,

132
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:05,120
I could clear myself of suspicion.

133
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,200
(Entrance)

134
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:08,600
I prepared night-vision glasses
and a poisoned needle that night

135
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:10,080
(Night-vision glasses. Instant death)
for the next day.

136
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,240
(Morning of April 7th)
On the morning of April 7th,

137
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:12,880
six new employees

138
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:14,480
joined us according to plan.

139
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:17,040
The new team leader
and I waited at the security entrance.

140
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,640
He seems respectful of me,

141
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,720
but in reality he was someone

142
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,950
Tui Nengzao had planted to monitor me.

143
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,200
I didn't dare reveal
any signs of betrayal.

144
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:26,800
I put on my usual stern act
toward the newcomers.

145
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,720
After exchanging the code,

146
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:32,000
everyone swiped their cards
and was assigned a channel at random.

147
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,920
(Channel display)
I got Channel Three.

148
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,360
Luckily it wasn't too far
from Channel One.

149
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,680
The night-vision glasses

150
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,720
would allow me to move freely.

151
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,120
Four new recruits and I

152
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,280
were the first to enter the channel.

153
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,560
I immediately put on
the night-vision glasses

154
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:45,520
and went to the corner.

155
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,720
I used the remote control

156
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,120
(Li)
to open the door just enough

157
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,880
for me to slip through

158
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:53,480
before the others reached the corners.

159
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,520
(Li)
Using the night-vision glasses,

160
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,520
I squeezed through the gap

161
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:58,400
from Door Three to Door Two,

162
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:00,720
(Li. Corpse)
then into Channel One's hidden area.

163
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,840
I drove the poisoned needle
into Tui Nengzao's heart.

164
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,640
I ended him on the spot.

165
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,280
(Corpse. Li)
After that, I quickly passed back

166
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,560
through to Channel Three

167
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:10,040
and restored the doors

168
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,080
to 90 degrees.

169
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,280
After both groups had passed through,

170
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,600
(Exit, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6: hidden door, exit)
I reset

171
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,440
the doors back to its original position.

172
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:18,280
This created the illusion

173
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:20,280
that the body had appeared
out of nowhere.

174
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,280
It perfectly concealed my crime.

175
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,240
After everyone left
with the head covers,

176
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,880
I stayed at the end of the line

177
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,880
(Night-vision glasses)
to destroy the remote.

178
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,500
Then I threw it into a corner

179
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:31,440
(Knockout drops)
near the exit

180
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,400
with the night-vision glasses

181
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,840
and Knockout drop.

182
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:35,800
After that,

183
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:38,680
I escorted the new recruits
to the briefing hall as usual

184
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,640
to attend the morning meeting.

185
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,800
I acted as though nothing had happened

186
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,440
while waiting for a chance
to escape the compound.

187
00:05:44,620 --> 00:05:46,860
(Player Liu Yuning log archive)

188
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,560
I'm player, Liu Yuning.

189
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,960
In this case, I play a barista

190
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:52,000
at Starlight Cafe,

191
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,080
Ning Bubble.

192
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,520
On the morning of April 7th,

193
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,720
I returned to the cafe.

194
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,880
After we brought Mei

195
00:05:57,880 --> 00:06:00,000
to the staff break room
the night before,

196
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,080
we agreed to meet here this morning

197
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,760
- to ask her
- Can you two get her out?

198
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,320
- the secret behind the cafe.
- Okay. Let's go.

199
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:06,800
We didn't expect

200
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,280
with Ke Coffee and Qian Jinding

201
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,360
- guarding the door,
- What happened?

202
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,480
we still failed.

203
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,480
- Mei wasn't in the break room.
- Mei is missing.

204
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,920
- What surprised me more
- Wait.

205
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,800
is that we found her body

206
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,200
What?

207
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,880
inside the secret passageway.

208
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,080
Was she tied up
and brought into the passage,

209
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,640
or did she enter it herself?

210
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:25,680
(Assessing the victim's last actions from the body's location)
Who could be so cruel to kill her?

211
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:28,680
At that moment, I could only take a guess.

212
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:29,960
Mei's death

213
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:32,360
had nothing to do with the four of us.

214
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,960
(Sorting out relationships)
We didn't kill Mei

215
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,760
(How did Tui Haomei leave?)
because we don't have grudges with her.

216
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:36,560
Yeah.

217
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,720
Very soon,

218
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,800
we found the work badge

219
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,920
she left behind on her.

220
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,660
(Supreme Phantom Dragonlord)

221
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,360
We realized she entered the passageway

222
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,200
on her own.

223
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,720
Using her badge,

224
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:48,720
we walked alone through
the pitch-black security channel

225
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:49,800
and arrived

226
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,240
at the AI compound.

227
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,360
Many people inside were being exploited.

228
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,520
To save them,

229
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,880
we could only obey and lie low

230
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,640
to investigate this.

231
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,960
To get rich, go crazy.

232
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:02,920
Do it all for the money.

233
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,560
Then,

234
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,680
we found a walkie-talkie
in the cafeteria.

235
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:08,440
The contents of the radio
confirmed my previous deduction.

236
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,640
Mei was killed

237
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,560
by the compound's boss, Tui Nengzao.

238
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,520
We also found out

239
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:17,960
that Tui Nengzao was dead too.

240
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,240
His corpse was discovered

241
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:21,160
inside the security channel.

242
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:24,920
But when we were inside the channel,

243
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,640
no one mentioned
seeing anything unusual.

244
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,220
(Post-channel review)
Could it be someone among us who did it?

245
00:07:30,220 --> 00:07:31,060
(Assessing for hidden killer)

246
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,000
There was no time to think.

247
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,160
The base activated
its self-destruct mode.

248
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,920
We would only enter the server room

249
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,760
and stop the program

250
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,640
to save the people.

251
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,880
During the process,

252
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:41,040
we also discovered

253
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:41,640
that I,

254
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,040
Jin Cardashian,

255
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,160
He Yiwei,

256
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,160
and Ding Pudding

257
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:48,920
had all been harmed by Tui Nengzao

258
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,640
and his AI compound.

259
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,960
The four of us had motives to kill him.

260
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,280
After escaping the base,

261
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:56,120
we returned to the crime scene.

262
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,800
Tui Nengzao died in Channel One

263
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:01,840
where Ding and Ke had walked through.

264
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,440
After that,

265
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,680
we found

266
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,280
the channel's blueprint
and Knockout drops.

